Repository Name Unauthorized: Dawson County Historical and Genealogical Society
Notes: Materials are kept in the Public Room of Dawson County Public Library.  Collection includes transcribed county histories, 1860-1910, microfilms of Rebekah Slaton Wilson's genealogical research materials, family histories, southern states history collection, census records, and materials for computer assisted genealogical research.  Published The Dawson County Heritage Book.  Historical and genealogical reference room in the Dawson Co. Library.
